## Description {#details}

Represents a particular available value that we know how to materialize.

Materialization of an <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/gvn/availablevalue">AvailableValue</a> never fails. An <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/gvn/availablevalue">AvailableValue</a> is implicitly associated with a rematerialization point which is the location of the instruction from which it was formed.

Definition at line 198 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/scalar/gvn-cpp">GVN.cpp</a>.
